    {
      "_id": 11325,
      "id": "the_bell_tolls_the_hunt_is_on",
      "name": "The Bell Tolls! The Hunt Is On!",
      "description": "Prune gently swings the Witchlure Bell, dealing <span style=\"color:#80FFD7FF\">Anemo DMG</span> to nearby opponents. After this, the Bell will enter the Hunter-Seeker mode.<br/><br/><span style=\"color:#FFD780FF\">Witchlure Bell: Hunter-Seeker</span><br/>In this mode, the Witchlure Bell will follow the current active character, attacking surrounding opponents at intervals and dealing <span style=\"color:#80FFD7FF\">AoE Anemo DMG</span>. This DMG is considered Elemental Burst DMG.",
